THE REAL ESTATE CENTER OF NEW BERN, INC

data.description: Turn-Key Three Bedroom Home with upstairs Bonus Room (potentially Bedroom 4!) located in desirable  Creekside School District! Enjoy the established & neighborly feel, the Side-Walks, plus nearby storage and shopping. Granite Countertops, Engineered HW Flooring, Fenced Yard, Upgraded 20x20 Patio and more...Architectural Shingles in 2018! Well cared for home minutes from Cherry Point or downtown historic New Bern; and a short drive to The Crystal Coast! Original owner. Welcome to the convenience and community of Longleaf Pines.
